{"title":"台湾纪行","authors":["李进才"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":9,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾纪行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李进才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夏，应台湾政治大学传播学院之邀，赴台参加“一九九三中文传播研究暨教学研讨会”，海内外２００多位华人学者与会，并游台岛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎黄快着鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中文传播赖钻研，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华人学者聚桃园。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炎黄何惧起步晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋起直追快着鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜宿阿里山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深林木屋静悄悄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斜晖如水夜月高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是小虫咝咝叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疑入仙乡至九霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欣游日月潭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日潭月潭日月潭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧波荡漾万山间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水依群峦多秀色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山赖湖光青欲燃。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}